{"tid":568231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[當你無到]【民間煙花匯演】士多變火藥庫 反黑掃場拉人 村民放煙花挑機","createTime":"2018-02-21T15:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T23:55:26.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2691783445df16f8e7f3397cb453acc7e0eab5c8","tid":568231,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:00:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180221/57859411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57859411&d=%2FaD7KDOFmFMMeKtofmtbWi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=36c447e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180221%2F57859411&h=f0febe00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180221/57859411</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 【22:25】警方在現場召開記者會期間，附近的李屋村有人燃放煙花，警方正展開調查。</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鑑於農曆新年期間，東九龍區內發生多宗違法燃放煙花事件，東九龍反黑組接手跟進，經深入調查及分析後，派員喬裝買家，於秀茂坪一天橋底下起出少量煙花。探員繼續追查煙花來源，終鎖定元朗洪水橋洪福邨附近一間士多出售有關煙花，今午5時許採取行動，帶同專門搜索爆炸品的搜索犬掩至該士多，在貨倉的天花及紙箱內搜出大批煙花爆竹，共重10公斤，總值約4千元。行動中，探員於士多內拘捕21歲姓姚及31歲姓郭男子，涉嫌非法藏有煙花爆竹。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，相信該士多由內地購入煙花爆竹，偷運來港出售圖利，估計已售出大部份的煙花。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方在現場召開記者會期間，附近的李屋村有人燃放煙花，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n踩入狗年由大年初一開始，香港各區都有人違規私自燃放煙花，包括觀塘樂華邨、荃灣大坡坊及屯門大興邨等，有網民笑指是「民間煙花匯演」，亦有市民指煙花非常靠近住宅爆開，甚至有煙花打入屋內，批評太危險。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法律第295章危險品條例第6條，非法藏有煙花爆竹的最高刑罰為罰款2萬5千元及監禁6個月。危險品（一般）規例第59條亦訂明，未領有許可証燃放或致使他人燃放煙花爆竹屬違法。"},{"pid":"122a9d9b98f7638005a8296a510077695e4ed5b2","tid":568231,"uid":12923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aab5e3f6081bc522f314b2c257113a47d55ac25","tid":568231,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d698a000df5c8cefea43d0a2b319377fc5ac4bc","tid":568231,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"咁串"},{"pid":"0c2c8ea2168385267b53212dda6a1c447d3e04bb","tid":568231,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"大家咁高咁大洗乜比面，特狗都要入飯局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774c8d0c423c48e4c1422cfe0300ce602c776e9f","tid":568231,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c2c8ea2168385267b53212dda6a1c447d3e04bb","tid":568231,"uid":30169,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"大家咁高咁大洗乜比面，特狗都要入飯局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"入黎"},{"pid":"3e50b82582879049fdd98fd6debaa7a1c7eeaf94","tid":568231,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8f8267382db92badc5c78f463ed86d99e836c34","tid":568231,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T20:59:33.000Z","msg":"圍頭狗咁寸都係俾黑警縱出黎"},{"pid":"e7a68332773528668f686e584591390e387887ee","tid":568231,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e8f8267382db92badc5c78f463ed86d99e836c34","tid":568231,"uid":171107,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T20:59:33.000Z","msg":"圍頭狗咁寸都係俾黑警縱出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T23:51:10.000Z","msg":"係港共政府，由僭建，到啡地"},{"pid":"63e412615b71b1af987a933d268865ba4d473a8c","tid":568231,"uid":23416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"死差狗惡得出咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s